    "description": {
      "value": "<p>The thrill of danger helps you to jump higher and farther. While you have @UUID[Compendium.pf2e-playtest-data.rr-playtest-class-features.Item.HAjDJbdawcI5TjTG]{Adrenaline}, you gain the following benefits.</p><ul><li>You gain climb and swim Speeds equal to half your land Speed.</li><li>The DCs of your @UUID[Compendium.pf2e.actionspf2e.Item.2HJ4yuEFY1Cast4h]{High Jumps} and @UUID[Compendium.pf2e.actionspf2e.Item.JUvAvruz7yRQXfz2]{Long Jumps} decrease by 10. This doesn't combine with other abilities that reduce those DCs.</li><li><p>The distance you can move with a vertical [[/act leap]] increases to 5 feet. Your distance for a horizontal Leap increases to 15 feet if your Speed is at least 15 feet, or to 20 feet if your Speed is at least 30 feet.</p><p></p></li></ul>",
